# This folder contains the request handlers, one per HTTP method + CGI.
# Example files to create here :
#
# IHandler.hpp => interface for all handlers implement handle
# GetHandler.hpp / .cpp => handles GET requests (serve static files)
# PostHandler.hpp / .cpp => handles POST requests (file upload)
# DeleteHandler.hpp / .cpp => handles DELETE requests (file deletion)
# CgiHandler.hpp / .cpp => handles CGI requests (fork + pipe + execve)
